content.text: Heyy! How's it going?
Doing pretty well, thanks for asking! How are you doing today?
I'm doing pretty good! Just got back from a sushi place.
Oh nice! I love sushi, where did you go?
It's a new place that just opened up near my house. It's called Sushi Yoshi.
Oh I've heard about that place! I've been meaning to try it.
You should definitely go! It's really good.
I will! Thanks for the recommendation!
No problem! What do you like to do for fun?
I love to watch movies, play music, and read comic books.
Oh cool! I love movies too. What's your favorite movie?
That's a tough question, but I think I'd have to say The Princess Bride.
That's a great movie! I love that movie too.
Yeah it's so good! What about you, what's your favorite movie?
I think my favorite movie is probably The Shawshank Redemption.
Oh that's a great movie too!
Yeah it is! I love the story and the characters.
Me too! It's such a good movie.
So what are you up to this weekend?
I'm not sure yet. I might go see a movie or something.
Oh cool! I might go see a movie too.
Maybe we could go see a movie together?
That would be fun! I'd love to go see a movie with you.
Great! I'll let you know what I decide.
Sounds good
